features:
BONUS SPACE AND CARRY: 
2 internal and 2 external pockets provide additional storage.

COMFY STRAPS: 
Best-in-class shoulder and waist straps for comfort and support even with the heaviest of payloads. Adjustable, stowable sternum strap. Waist and shoulder straps instantly stow away beneath magnetically sealed flaps.

SUPERIOR ACCESS: 
An extra long zipper path provides wider access than traditional duffels for easier packing and total visibility.

EXPANDS AND CONTRACTS: 
Fit more in with impressive expansive storage that ranges between 45L to 65L via 2 external expansion zips.

ULTIMATE PROTECTION: 
Weatherproof, 100% recycled 600D nylon canvas shell with high-visibility grey interior.
Oversized #10 weatherproof zip. Built-in theft-deterrent main and size zipper pull locks.

GEAR COMPATIBLE: 
Dedicated Capture Clip (sold separately) attachments points on shoulder and waist straps.
Designed to fit Peak Design Packing Tools (up to 4 units of Packing and/or Camera cubes).

CONVENIENT GRAB POINTS: 
6 padded grab handles on the sides, ends, and top of the bag enable convenient grab and go.
